et laserlys avdekke hva man ser i rommet, sier Reinsberg M\u00f8rch.", "Trondheim Kunstmuseum, Gr\u00e5m\u00f8lna, s\u00f8ndag 22. januar. Utstillingen blir st\u00e5ende til 7. mai."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "da5d005c2cd3d7bfa09640d5ff9c429877eeec821a92f220884af72356c19112"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-01-17T08:57:01.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Trondheim Kunstmuseum starter \u00e5ret med utstillingen \u00abDeltakelse\u00bb der hovedverket er Yoko Onos \u00abWish Tree\u00bb"}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/kultur/article14069064.ece/mjpk5r/ALTERNATES/w980-default/graa.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/b4350202a3022416276f44ea82ec5f6c3e3462a4.jpg?596c9e5c"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Vi mailet med Yoko Ono for \u00e5 f\u00e5 oppskriften p\u00e5 kunstverket -adressa.no", "\u00d8nsker fra hele verden", "Mailet med Yoko Ono", "Publikum kan delta i kunsten", "Nytt verk"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "b4350202a3022416276f44ea82ec5f6c3e3462a4"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Trondheim Kunstmuseum", "Gr\u00e5m\u00f8lna", "Kunst"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Trondheim Kunstmuseum,Gr\u00e5m\u00f8lna,Kunst"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["publikum", "kunstverk", "utstillingen", "verk", "kunst"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["imagine peace tower", "vi\u00f0ey", "deltakelse", "kunstmuseets", "trondheim kunstmuseum", "gr\u00e5m\u00f8lna", "wish tree"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["reykjav\u00edk", "japan", "reinsberg", "island"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["john lennons", "ida gr\u00